title: Brady Quinn on holdouts, AFC South position battles (Football 7/26)
description:
Will Brinson and Brady Quinn break down Sterling Shepard's injury (2:45), the latest Madden game (5:45), Ezekiel Elliott skipping the Cowboys team flight (8:45), Michael Thomas wanting $20M (16:30), Brady's holdout from 2007 and rookies who just signed (18:50). Then the guys break down positional battles in the AFC South (26:30).
